data.description: You will absolutely Love calling this place Home.  Just picture everyone with their own bedroom in this 4 bedroom 2 bath house.  It has an open floor plan whick makes it great for gatherings so that no one feels left out of the fun.   High vaulted ceiling in the main area and large windows in the front of back for added natural light.  You will also enjoy the great curb appeal and the nice thick green grass located off of the back patio.  Seller has installed nice sod in the front and half of the backyard and a metal fence in the front and sides of half of the backyard.  These additions will save you thousands of dollars
